The paper focuses on privacy preservation in machine learning, specifically in the context of attribute inference attacks. This suggests that the paper is likely to fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper may also fall under the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV) due to the experimental evaluation of different privacy preservation algorithms.
